yir 0.1

resource cpu0 cpu.arm64
resource fabric0 data.fabric
resource shader0 shader.render

cpu.const_i64 seed cpu0 4
cpu.const_i64 inc cpu0 3
cpu.add sum cpu0 seed inc
data.move sum_on_shader fabric0 sum shader0
shader.dispatch shaded shader0 sum_on_shader
shader.print done shader0 shaded

edge dep seed sum
edge dep inc sum
edge xfer sum sum_on_shader
edge xfer sum_on_shader shaded
edge dep shaded done
edge effect shaded done
